# @brief Flatten a list
# @param _L the list to work on
# @details The original list is not modified.
# =begin
# (let cool [[1 2 3] [4] 5 6 [7 8] 9])
# (print (flatten cool))  # [1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9]
# =end
# @author https://github.com/SuperFola
